      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-KJL0018-SELECT-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    WK-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD
                         WK-PRDCT-MEDM-CLSFI-CD
                         WK-PRDCT-TMPLT-CD
